假、冇大假睇住自己個大肚婆？明明係社會嘅錯，點解要我讓位比佢坐？<br />\n<br />\n大肚婆冇位坐，我地毒撚連女仔手都未拖過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 公平咩，坐坐坐，有錢坐的士養車先生仔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 窮人生仔正仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2c8dfda939fd6f6d766c2ca6eda269d95eddb11e","tid":461070,"uid":52068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:40:30.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"fcf0e433e279174d18bdaefddc5f3337aaf65bc4","tid":461070,"uid":30988,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:41:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>孕婦捕捉器</blockquote><br />\n孕婦 = 人地女人<br />\n單身女子 = potential自己女人<br />\n<br />\n男人有資源(座位)而讓畀前者明顯違反生物本性🤔</blockquote><br />\n其中一種最有力嘅生物本性係照顧弱小孕婦<br />\n因為呢種特質可以提高族群嘅存續率<br />\n連貓狗老虎都會照顧幼小(個本性強到連他族嘅幼小都會照顧)"},{"pid":"cd3fbc0443930f3265f15b81fc3cb6f618bca5ec","tid":461070,"uid":35870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />幾正"},{"pid":"1531fc3d73568ee8e3e584ebcd21af77c77e81b0","tid":461070,"uid":19213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"225da89d2c3dfd96355103b4169d8bf29970a650","tid":461070,"uid":93784,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:53:55.000Z","msg":"日本 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n的確避免左尷尬既情況 <br />\n但係相對情況唔能夠套落香港<br />\n因為當你香港人想讓坐個陣點知黎左件支那大肚婆<br />\n跟住佢身邊個老公都係支那人 屌雙非 你即刻想del app"},{"pid":"1c9c798a7313ec8029dc679add84c564ecdec650","tid":461070,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-07T10:55:31.000Z","msg":"係咪毒撚諗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif